thread.title_full: Dominidesign Beoordeeld door Troels Vejen Christensen

author: Troels Vejen Christensen
title: Troels Vejen Christensen
text:
Very nice furniture.
We ordered 6 y-chairs and the quality is very nice.
The chairs has a few very small scratches, in places you only see if you turn the chairs upside down, soo nothing noticeable.
You would have to pay about 3-4 times as much if you wanted to buy similar quality chairs in Denmark.
Delivery took around 1 month.
The delivery was due around the 16.2 and we got the chairs on the 20.2.
Via the tracking number, we could follow how far the delivery was.
So I would recommend this shop to others, very nice quality for the right price.
